title: Some Results on Coefﬁcient Estimate Problems for Four-Leaf-Type Bounded Turning Functions
content: Let BT4l denotes a subclass of bounded turning functions connected with a four-leaf-type domain. The goal of the study is to probe into coefﬁcients of |b6|, |b7|, |b8|, the bounds of the logarithmic coefﬁcients and the third-order determinants of H3,1, H3,2, H3,3 for functions in this class.
